value.string: Affordable East end home about 14 miles from town. This cute 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath was just recently painted inside and out. Laminent flooring was installed in living room and new vinyl in bathrooms. Located in a nice quiet neighborhood on the east side of Molokai. Home is close to the elementary school, small neighborhood store and many great east end beaches. Ride bikes along the country road. Currently rented long term so call for showings. Listor is a licensed Broker in Hawaii.

Price improvement! Slow down and step back in time on the quiet isle of Lana'i. Three bed room, two bath home on a spacious lot that exceeds zoning requirements for ohana construction. Located on a peaceful cul-de-sac with front yard opening into large back yard area. Solar water heater AND 6 photovoltaic panel system qualified for MECO 2% net metering. Enjoy the convenience of a ramp leading you to a covered back porch, then a deck with hot tub ... perfect for relaxing while enjoying our beautiful island weather! Orchid shelter and tropical trees add to the outdoor experience. Washer and dryer conveniently located behind doors inside the carport. Front entrance includes a screened in sun room. The living room and tastefully remodeled kitchen are spacious and feature upgraded cabinets, granite counter tops, full top custom butcher block, touch faucet, and new dishwasher w. 10-year warranty. The master bathroom has two walk in showers, one handicap accessible. Second bathroom includes tub. There are plenty of double pane vinyl slider windows for terrific natural light.
